45
00:03:09,950 --> 00:03:16,520
The neutral leptons, the neutrinos,
are produced in radioactive decays.

46
00:03:16,520 --> 00:03:19,110
They have zero electric charge and
they're very small mass.

47
00:03:21,160 --> 00:03:24,230
