53
00:03:45,040 --> 00:03:50,390
Every family has three generations, almost
identical copies of the first one, but

54
00:03:50,390 --> 00:03:51,740
a lot heavier than the first one.

55
00:03:52,780 --> 00:03:55,550
In the first generation,
we find the familiar electron,

56
00:03:55,550 --> 00:03:59,110
the light neutrino nu_L,
the quarks up and down u and d,

57
00:03:59,110 --> 00:04:03,300
