the ordinary matter around us today.

58
00:04:04,640 --> 00:04:10,190
The second generation, has the muon µ,
the medium mass neutrino nu_M,

59
00:04:10,190 --> 00:04:14,900
the charm quark and
the strange quark, c and s.

60
00:04:14,900 --> 00:04:20,780
And finally, in the third
generation we find the tau lepton,

61
00:04:20,780 --> 00:04:24,530
the heavy neutrino nu_H,
the top and bottom quarks, t and b.

62
00:04:25,690 --> 00:04:28,340
There is a quantum number
which is called flavor which

63
00:04:28,340 --> 00:04:31,550
distinguishes between
the generations inside each family.

64
00:04:31,550 --> 00:04:35,346
It is conserved by all interactions
except the weak interactions.

65
00:04:38,067 --> 00:04:40,980
